headline: Why Tariffs Could Cost Far More Than We Might Think
summary: There are many words that can describe all of the tariffs -- potential tariffs, retaliatory tariffs -- but one word in particular strikes fear in investors: Uncertainty.  Here's the kicker: We've mostly been calculating the tariffs simply based on the 25% slapped on imported vehicles.  What we haven't heard much about recently, at least when it comes to tariff issues, is plant shutdowns.
